<div class="page-banner">
  <div class="title-container">
    <h1><strong>Linkedin</strong></h1>
    <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2016/11/18/11/16/social-1834011_1280.png" style="width: 150px;height: 150px;">
    <h1>cyber-image</h1>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="container social-media-pages">
  <div class="card-title">
    <h1>Profile</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="card-details d-flex">
    <div class="twin-1 w-50">
      <h3 style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Avatar</h3>
      <%= image_tag "https://kitt.lewagon.com/placeholder/users/ssaunier", class: "avatar dropdown-toggle", style:"width:120px;", id: "navbarDropdown", data: { toggle: "dropdown" }, 'aria-haspopup': true, 'aria-expanded': false %>
      <p>Studies have found that your LinkedIn profile is <strong>40% more likely</strong> to be clicked on if it contains a profile picture. Add yours!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="twin-2 w-50">
      <h3 style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Connections</h3>
      <p>You have <strong>100 connections</strong>.<br>It's not much, find more people you know!</p>
      <p>Your headline :<strong>Teacher at @LeWagon</strong>.</p>
      <p>Your search zone : <strong>Lyon and Greater Paris</strong> </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="twin-cards d-flex">
    <div class="twin-1 w-50 mr-3">
      <div class="card-title">
        <h1>Experiences</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="card-details">
        <h3 style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Last experience</h3>
        <p>Your last job ended in <strong>2018</strong>. Update your profile, tell the employers what you've been doing!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="twin-2 w-50">
      <div class="card-title">
        <h1>Education</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="card-details">
        <h3 style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Diploma level</h3>
        <p>Your last/current diploma is <strong>Sustainable project management</strong>. Is this correct ?</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card-title">
    <h1>Skills</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="card-details">
    <p>Everyone has skills! Add skills so that recruiters can spot you according to what they need.</p>
    <hr>
    <%= @profiles %>
    <hr>
    <%= @skills %>
    <hr>
    <%= @educations %>
    <hr>
    <%= @connections %>
  </div>

  <div class="social-link text-center">
    <h3><i class="fas fa-arrow-circle-down"></i> Click to make changes <i class="fas fa-arrow-circle-down"></i></h3>
    <%= link_to '', "https://www.linkedin.com/#{current_user.username_insta}", target:"_blank", style:"text-decoration: none;", class:"fab fa-fw fa-linkedin" %>
  </div>

   <div class="text-center">
    <%= link_to "Back to Dashboard", dashboard_path, class:"btn btn-back" %>
    </div>

</div>

